social_posts.post_text: Dear Fighters, You Gotta Invest In Yourself……
I Usually don’t make Post Like this, But like Niece Bella is 2 Years Old Today and I just wanted to Share Her Cuteness With the World..

Today is officially my 18 Year “Boyfriend/Girlfriend” Anniversary (almost 11 years married) @livving4us  Still won’t admit it that she asked me to be her boyfriend before I asked her to be my girlfriend, but it’s cool to think at how far we’ve come together and all the Smiles we’ve Had along the way… 😘😘❤️❤️
Do Not Pass Go, Do Not Collect $200!!!
This is what 18 Years together looks like 😘❤️😘 @livving4us
I’m just here working on my fitness and minding my business, but I didn’t forget the way y’all was acting over them chicken sandwiches 🤦🏾‍♂️🤦🏾‍♂️

DON’T DO IT!!
Reconsider!!!

The Team Finished the Year Strong, We Went to Louisiana and @_ia823 & @officialteteo  picked up 2 Belts, My Guy @ogg.__ Lost a Close decision to a tough opponent (in his own city).. My Team went 7-3 against the Teams in our Division this year and I’m extremely proud of everyone who stepped in the ring this year…
Grandpa Gainz Can’t move as much weight as I used to, but I was still able to take 315 & 335lbs for a ride today 💪🏾💪🏾💪🏾

As A Trainer Being Able to Process the Habits in the ring of your opponent and give instructions to your fighter in real time is ESSENTIAL to winning fights… Great Job by @officialteteo  Following corner instructions and picking up the Easy Win…

Candid Coaching Moments…
Blessed to Have an Opportunity to Build this solid group of Young People… It’s Bigger than Boxing, we’re building a family….

#Gainz #Gains #Gainzrus #Gainzrusfitness #Fitness #Gainzboxing #Gainzboxingclub #Boxing #Boxing101 #BoxingCoach #NoBoxingNoLife

Happy 21st B-Day @officialteteo  I’m grateful for the opportunity to be a trainer to be a part of your boxing career… Now you can “Legally” drink, but don’t drink too much we still got more work to do and more fights to win!!!!
Grandpa Gainz Ain’t been hitting heavy weights lately, but I got my lifting partner @ogg.__  And @averiiona Trolling Me and that’s all the motivation I need to get back on Track 💪🏾💪🏾💪🏾💪🏾

Sparring is the most important ingredient in the process of developing a boxer.. It’s the time when you can really see how well the fighter is understanding the principles you’ve taught them…. You’ll never learn how to drive sitting in a parked car…
Christmas 2022 was a success!!!
2022 was my best year Professionally as a trainer/boxing coach… Now I’m Recharged, Rested & Ready to have an even better year in 2023..
Sometimes I get Stressed & Depressed when things in life don’t go the way I plan it…. But then I realize my Ex is fat with 2 kids and lives with her Mom and I get back happy again……
There Won’t Be Any Bullying Happening with these 2….. @ericaperica09  At Least You know he’s not mad at you…..

This is an example of ELITE Corner work by @buddymcgirtboxing  Our #1 Priority is to make sure our fighters don’t get hurt, and to also give them SPECIFIC INSTRUCTIONS on how to handle any situation that happens throughout the course of the Bout…. Gatti went on to Box Beautifully and win with a fractured hand, Buddy Coached him through the injury!!!
The Choices You Make Outside The Ring Are Sometimes more important than what Happens in the Ring….. Choose Wisely….

social_posts.post_text:
One of the Best Parts of the Job is when an Athlete Believes in what you’re telling them in the gym and executes it in real competition…. Being a “shorter” fighter for her weight class the overhand right is a big part of her Arsenal and she was able to go “Over-The-Top” and win a belt in doing so!! 

Great Work @anneliseh21 We Just gotta keep that right hand up!!!
Why would worry about people giving me my flowers and I wake up everyday and see Palm Trees????

Throughout the Course of the last 9 Months My Competition Boxing Team has done 9 Events and Seeing the Fighters “Happy” Makes all the Long Nights in the gym Make Sense.. Behind Every Belt, Medal & Trophy it’s nights of me in the gym Sweeping Floors, Mopping up Blood and Disinfecting Gloves, and Trust me it’s all Worth it!!

social_posts.post_text:
(Long Post Alert)

In 2020 Ms. Tracy was a client at one of my Beack Body Weight-Loss Classes, then because of Covid-19 and all the Various Social Distancing & Vaccine Mandates we lost about 1 year of workout time… When she came back she said she wanted to lose weight and become a bodybuilder… I thought she was joking, but to my surprise she said it was her goal to step on a bodybuilding stage at 60 Years Old… With the help of one of the best posing coaches in the world @reginaperezfitness  Ms. Tracy lost about 40lbs and stepped on stage yesterday and placed Top 5 in EVERY DIVISION!!!!! 

(I’ll have the “official stage shots to post later)

One Day It’ll All Make Sense…….

#Gainz #Gainzrus #Gainzrusfitness #gainzboxingclub #GainzSquad #Boxing #boxingtraining #boxingworkout #BoxingCoach
From Beginners to Fighters on the path to going Pro EVERYBODY is Grinding, and I’m gonna do my part to get the best outta each athlete that steps in the gym….
Some of the most important moments as a coach are things said to the fighters OUTSIDE of the ring.. Competitive Boxing is not a game… You Don’t Play boxing…
Good Dope Sells Itself….
I lost 3 of My Best Fighters in 2022, and I regrouped and retooled and we are bigger and better than Every… 🦍🦍🦍🦍

I am really proud of this young champ, He reached out to me for some online coaching to make sure he was Ready Ready for his first tournament and I was throughly impressed that he took notes on his white board to remember everything we worked on…  Congratulations & Job Well Done Champ @_rayanaidel_ 💯💥💪🏾🥊

Drills Drills Drills!!!
Building & Developing This Team 1 Workout at a Time…
Feliz Cumpleaños To My Guy @jordanmenez_444  I’m blessed to be a part of your journey to become a Professional Boxer… Enjoy Your Birthday Amigo!! BAILAMOS!!! 🥊🇲🇽🕺🏾🎉

My Wife is outta town right now so this will be the first Valentine’s Day In the last 17 years that we didn’t spend together, I was just looking at some of our Valentine’s Day Date night pictures for the memories…. Happy Long Distance Valentine’s Day @livving4us

Atlanta Photo Dump:
I was able to spend some time with my brothers @mustafasboxing & @grindhousecoachc and meet their 14 Year old KILLER @thechamp_jace  @anneliseh21 was able to compete in the @buckheadfightclub and I went to @barveganatl  Its always a good time when I hit the ATL.. I’ll be back in 3 weeks!!!
Big Shout out to @shotsbydabuddy28  For Capturing these great Shots at the @gainzboxingclub

D.C. Photo Dump

Sometimes you wanna go where everybody knows your name, and they’re always glad you came….

ATL Photo Dump…

Congrats to @jordanmenez_444 For Winning the GA Golden Gloves, And Thanks to @sugarbertboxing for giving us the opportunity and @mustafasboxing for letting us get in the last shakeout at the Grindhouse… Be back in Atlanta in 3 weeks to pick up some belts!!
We doing a lot more than Boxing at the @gainzboxingclub Our Morning Classes Will help you get that body ready for Summer!!!

We are going to start Promoting our Kid’s Fit Camp soon and it’s important for the kids and parents to know there is no “fighting” allowed inside the Ring… We let the kids spar (if their parent’s are present or consent) but sparring is not a “fight,” it’s the time to practice the skills you’ve learned in training…

Sparring is not a fight…
The Emerald Coast Of Florida hasn’t Been a Boxing Hub in a Long Time, Trust me we are out to change that one Workout at a Time!!
Don’t Believe me, Just Watch….
A Family Doesn’t Need to be Perfect, it just needs to be United…

It is with Utter Sadness and despair that I am informing the world my wife has Peacefully Transitioned Today.. She Fought Valiantly in a Coma for 6 Days but unfortunately her body was unable to survive. It Gives me Great Joy To know Our Daughter and I was with her until she took her final breath and she was surrounded by her immediate family, friends and Loved Ones during her last moments.. Please Allow us Time and Privacy to Process this Loss and we will share the information on her Candlelight Vigil and Home-going Services Soon……

Til Death Do Us Part
4/7/23
4:47pm
💔💔💔💔💔💔💔
Day 1……
Day 2…..
Day 3…

Unfortunately Due to Izac’s Opponent not having his passbook and their Weight’s being 1.5lb too far away per the USABOXING Guidelines he was not able to compete for a belt this weekend, but @esboxing_club was nice enough to let the boys still fight on the card and I am forever grateful because he didn’t have to…. My Momma was too busy being my assistant coach/cheerleader for us to get any footage of the fight but both kid’s performed great and got a Big Ovation From The Crowd…
Day 7……

Day 8…… 

We had the Sunset Vigil for my wife last and the Rain Slowed up just in time to give us a pretty Sunset… Thanks for everyone who came!!

Blessed for the opportunity to be a positive influence in my community through the sport of boxing……

Gainz

social_posts.post_text: Annelise Opponent got “sick” 3 days before the event, so unfortunately she wasn’t able to Compete but my Guy Dave Wanted me to work His Corner and we were able to pick up  a 30-27 Unanimous Decision Victory Yesterday in Tampa!!
My Wife’s Final Services will be held at Ft. Lincoln Funeral this Saturday at 12:30pm….
Lost…….

First of all Thank You for allowing us to use your magnificent space to host my Wife’s Party @maibrotherskeeper  And Thank You @lgweds  @djpoloent & @mixwitluv  For Playing a major part in the event being a success….

Now it’s time to Heal….
@bren_dazed Thank You for your contribution to help out, I really appreciate it… But We Got Food at the house!!!!
The Way My Checkings & Savings are set up I might need to start selling drugs or start a Gofundme to support my daughters Travel Habits…
My Kid is the Strongest Person I Know…

Single Dad Life Be Like…..
I Gave her money to go outside, she took the money and still didn’t leave 😩😩
It feels good to be back to work and trying to get my life back to Normal… Right now the gym is my Safe Space and I’m grateful to have a team full of athletes who are working HARD!!!

We Made it Thru Prom and once all the pictures were done and everybody left the house and the kids made it back Safely I Cried like a baby, But this time it wasn’t Tears of Sadness they were tears of Joy Because I know my Queen was Happy Seeing Our Princess so Happy… Next Up is Graduation…
1 Month In, A Lifetime to go…..
The Crazy thing about Memories is part of you is sad that you’ll never get to experience some things again and part of you feels happy you got a chance to experience the memorable moments…. 💔😢💔😢💔😢

What I’ve learned over the last 6 weeks it’s that there is no blueprint on how to grieve, everyone tries their best to cope and deal with their emotions differently.. My Therapist told me don’t try to “buy” my way out of grief and make crazy purchases, but I bought a necklace 😩😩 Serenity has been trying her best to deal with things her own way, and yesterday she drove by someone selling Puppies so meet the newest member of our family.. Hennessy Relly Nash 🐶🐶
Cheers to all the Mother’s….

Great Weekend In New Orleans, I was able to go out and touch the city a little bit (I even learned a new world) and the team was able to bring home a belt from the @getcharightboxing Show on Saturday… I love the people and the culture of NOLA and I’ll be right back there soon!!!
Back in the Gym After picking up a Belt Saturday in New Orleans, we are drilling the BASICS!! @jordanmenez_444 is Great with his Counters and we got 6 weeks until the next fight to get even Better….
You can live thru anything if Magic Made It…..
Against all the obstacles in her way she did it!!! Congrats to @serenitys_world_  And all of the other Graduates of the 2023 Class of Crestview High School!!
It’s not the same……

Yesterday I took a Memorial Day Weekend Boat Trip like we do every year. The Water was nice and warm and the beach was Pretty and peaceful, but it’s not the same without my Co-Captain riding with me… I made sure I poured my wife a drink on her favorite spot on the beach…… Life Be Lifing, but Life Goes on 😢😭

I really just wanna lay down in the grass all day…. This is harder than I thought.. But I’m trying to process things slowly and learn to accept my reality… I feel ALONE but I know I have a support system of people who care for me, This is Tough…
The Nerve of these people who actually are swimming at the damn Swimming Pool… They must don’t know I’m on vacation…..
May Photodump: April was one of the most difficult months of my life and Thankfully I was able to spend time with my family and friends in May to Slowly begin to adjust to my “New Life”
2 Months… I’m OK, But I Don’t Know…..

She needs me more than ever..
I need her more than ever…
We all we got 
@serenitys_world_

@_ia823  Boxed Beautifully Over the weekend and he’s well on his way to becoming a professional, The Defense, Jab, Range Control, & Feints are right where it needs to be… The Name of the Game is Hit and Don’t Get Hit!!

@israel_cortes1  Boxed Beautifully Yesterday In a nice little tune-up to get ready for the Junior Golden Gloves… He’s only 14 and has a NICE feel for the ring and he knows how to remain calm and fight his fight…. Once we get him better on the inside and increase that punch output he’s gonna be even Better!! Very Proud of him!!

Little Moments, Big Memories…
@serenitys_world_
3 Months Later, Still Trying to Figure it out…

Big Thank you to @esboxing_club for allowing my team to compete on the card yesterday and for Coach Dude to come help me in the corner because my assistant Coach Couldn’t Make it!!

I’ll post the official fight pics and some videos tomorrow 🔥🔥🔥

I am Super Proud of my team making the 5 Hour trip to compete against some TOUGH Opponents in their own backyard. And a big Thank You to @esboxing_club for allowing us on the card and @harrywymanphoto for this Amazing Photography!!

Big Thank You to the @spartanboxingclubnola  For Allowing my Team to Compete on Card On Saturday and for always showing love, And much love to our extended Texas family @2sharpnorris & @kingjulian361 

Can’t wait to do it again in October!!!
It’s Crazy How Life can Be… 100 Days ago I took the biggest loss of my life Losing my Wife, but today my Brand is bigger than ever but I still feel so alone inside….. Life Be Lifin, But Life Goes on…
You can live through anything if Magic Made it….

I’m soooooo Proud Of Lisey, She Took 2 Tough Losses in Atlanta and bounced back nicely last weekend in Louisiana and then beat a Girl who was 6 Inches Taller and with more experience in her first fight with 3:00 rounds in the open class.. 1 Win Down 3 More to Go!! @anneliseh21  @gainzboxingclub @usaboxing
Much Love & Respect @pedty_murphy  No Matter How Strong We Are Grief is still tough to deal with…

We went 2-1 this week (we was supposed to fight Friday but our Opponent Couldn’t Pass a Physical) Big Thank you to all the People from @usaboxing  for putting on an Amazing Event!!!
July Photo-dump… July was a BUSY month, we put 10 fighters into the Ring in 4 different States and we walked away with Wins everywhere we went!! Grandpa out here Working!!!
Them Delgado Brother Back in the Lab!!! @_jdelgado_  Just picked up his first win and he’s Hungry for More and @kingjulian361 is still on the throne at 165lbs!!!! Great work @angelalpiazza 🔥🦍🔥🦍

@anneliseh21 Picking up 2 wins at the National Women’s Tournament has me focused on continuing to build and develop my female athletes… 3 Different Age Groups, Skill Levels & Weight Classes and they are all getting Better…

Even Though She Didn’t win the Tournament I am sooooooo Proud Of Kaitlyn!! She’s only been boxing for 3 months and she’s Sparred Grown Women and Boys to get ready to compete at the Junior Golden Gloves… She took on 2 Tough Opponents from Texas and we came up a little short, but most importantly we got the Thumbs Up from Momma that her Baby is a FIGHTER!!!!!!
Orlando Photo Dump…. I was able to get some Much Needed Rest & Relaxation after the fights were over and I got to touch the City a Little!!

Big Thank You to @glacierbodies for putting on a great & well run show at the @ocbfireandiceclassic!! Ms. Tracy was able to pick up some hardware in 3 categories against a stacked class!! Thank you to @_beautyinbeastmod_ & @reginaperezfitness For Always doing an Amazing Job!!!

Constantly Building & Developing these Fighters, offense always begins and with a quick and powerful jab and a strong cross to “hurt” the opponent… All the hooks & uppercuts come later!!

Great work!!

Happy 18th Birthday to my Big Baby @serenitys_world_ 
I am proud of the young woman you’ve grown up to be and just know your mom is smiling down from Heaven proud of you as well!!!

My Baby is officially the “Big 18” and the best part of her Celebration was seeing her sign the paperwork to officially be a Homeowner, this is a plan her momma put in motion years in advance and I’m happy to see it come to fruition!! Congrats Brick!! @serenitys_world_

Another Safe and Successful Trip for the Team!! We were able to go 3-1 against 4 TOUGH opponents and had a blast performing at a great venue in front of a great crowd…. We Back in Action in 2 weeks in Orlando!!!

@israel_cortes1  Boxed Beautifully On Saturday getting his opponent outta there in the 1st Round.. The Kid has a bright future in the sport, he’s only 14 and can box out of both stances and he understands how to “Set Up” his power shots and doesn’t get hit with Unnecessary punches in exchanges…. It’s only his 2nd Fight but he boxes like he’s more experienced… @m_cortes17 Your Son is REALLY Good!!!
Izac is only 10 years old, this is his 4th fight and he listened and followed the gameplan Perfectly this Saturday!! He scored his first knockdown and a Unanimous Decision victory!!
Weekend Photo Dump, Boxing & Brunching.. Pooling & Cooling

I am a firm believer that “Thoughts Become Things,” I turned an idea and a prayer from my mom into the biggest competition boxing team on the Emerald Coast Of Florida…. And I’m just getting started..

@gainzboxingclub

Great Time Today at @sandboxvr  We completed 2 missions and I can’t wait to come back to do the Squid Games Mission!!
@serenitys_world_

Sunsets are 1 thing I’ll never get enough of!!

@paradiseadventurespcb

I’m not a “Business Man” I’m a BUSINESS man, let me handle my Business Damn!!

@pete_da_photographer
@_jdelgado_  Won his last fight by Decision, he’s already prematched for his next fight in a couple weeks… We back in the lab making sure this one won’t go to the Judges 🦍🦍🦍
From the Kids, To the Amateurs to the athletes with the Aspirations of going pro everything begins and ends with Mastering the Basics…

It’s nothing like evenly matched sparring…
2 men, same weight class, same skill level pushing each other to see who’s better….

The question is if you was a judge who won the round???

We do ALOT of Drills in the @gainzboxingclub  But everything revolves around Sparring… The Guys aren’t trying to hurt each other every round but the best way to ready for real fights is to deal with real punches…

@josiahhboyd

Another Safe and Successful Trip For the Team!! @jordanmenez_444  Scored a Unanimous Decision win against a TOUGH Opponent in a very crowd pleasing match and Won “Fighter of the Night” & @navia.hopkins lost a CLOSE 29-28 Split Decision in her first fight against a very very tough opponent… Thanks to @orlandoboxingclub For Allowing us on the card and giving us a chance to compete!!!

One of the Best Feelings in the sport is beating someone in their own gym/city… My Team Travels a lot to make sure we are always getting work against Top Tier Competition, and @jordanmenez_444 Was up to the task of going to War against a TOUGH Puerto Rican Opponent in front of his Fans!!!
The Face Change but the Grind Remains the same!!! We Working Over Here!!!

As a Coach I only have :50 between rounds to explain the Strengths/Weaknesses/Tendencies of the opponent… It didn’t take me long to see The Fighter always Dipped his Head to the right when a jab came his way and he was right in the line of fire for the Uppercut… Great Job by @jordanmenez_444 Listening to the Corner instructions and executing it Perfectly… 🦍🦍🦍
The Energy in the gym has been GREAT lately, all Ages, all weight classes and all skill levels are working HARD!!!
It’s the Circle Of Life…

Still Here…

Still Him…
I really love this job!!! For Every Competition fighter from my team you see winning real fights there are also beginners who are just trying to have fun and learn the basics…

I can Show you better than I can Tell You…..

@pete_da_photographer
Sometimes You Don’t Know The Value of a Moment Until it Becomes a Memory…
Rule #1 Protect Yourself At All Times!!!!

Happy Birthday to @anneliseh21  We’ve Won Together, We’ve Loss Together, We’ve Laughed Together and We’ve Cried together (well she cried and I just did a bunch of cursing) But I’m so Grateful to say that I’m her Coach… She’ll fight a bear if it weighs under 145lbs and had on 12oz Gloves!! Enjoy your Day Lisey, but not too much because we have more fights to win!! 🦍🦍🦍

Teaching the sport of boxing to kids can be fun and equally challenging at times, but it’s no better feeling than when a child “gets it!”
